descriptionHtml:
The entrance \"The Rabbit Hole\" is located behind the first house in Winterhold (next to the tree and snowbank). 
*Rabbit Hole door FIXED!* SAVE backup files just in case! 
___________________________________________ 
*Revisions 1 & 2 - (rugs, Giant mushrooms and instruments in the rabbit hole, and a small midway house connecting rabbit hole and mansion). I won\'t do much more due to serious health issues. 

*Revision 3 - The switch for Shadowmere has been moved in front of his \"tiny room\". Not in room, but reachable. 

*REVISION 4 - Giant shields placed on the wall near the weapon racks, a few E.E. crates replacing old boring ones, Wolf\'s Bane silver sword damage slightly upped, and a workbench added near the forge.
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
Notes from Creator- 
I have fixed many (not all) cracks between x,y,z. It\'s near impossible to get them all when you make some areas from scratch. 
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 

HaVe FuN! :}
